      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/Search\" title=\"Search\">Search</a> * <a href=\"/Node\" title=\"Node\">Node</a> * Leaf Node</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:251px;\"><a href=\"http://www.mcescher.com/Gallery/back-bmp/LW356.jpg\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/d/d9/EschersDewdrop.jpg\" width=\"249\" height=\"188\" class=\"thumbimage\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:EschersDewdrop.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div><a href=\"/Category:M._C._Escher\" title=\"Category:M. C. Escher\">M. C. Escher</a>, Dewdrop, 1948 <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Leaf nodes</b> are <a href=\"/Node\" title=\"Node\">nodes</a> with no further successors. They are either <a href=\"/Terminal_Node\" title=\"Terminal Node\">terminal nodes</a> or nodes where the desired <a href=\"/Depth\" title=\"Depth\">depth</a> from the <a href=\"/Root\" title=\"Root\">root</a> is accomplished and which has been assigned a heuristic value as an \"educated guess\" to an approximate of a terminal value. Each <a href=\"/Search_Tree\" title=\"Search Tree\">search tree</a> has at least one leaf node. \n</p>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Leaf_Node&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: See also\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Horizon_Node\" title=\"Horizon Node\">Horizon Node</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Interior_Node\" title=\"Interior Node\">Interior Node</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Node_Types#LeafNodes\" title=\"Node Types\">Leaves of Node Types</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Quiescent_Node\" title=\"Quiescent Node\">Quiescent Node</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Terminal_Node\" title=\"Terminal Node\">Terminal Node</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Leaf_Node&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Leaf_node\">Leaf node from Wikipedia</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Category:Klaus_Schulze\" title=\"Category:Klaus Schulze\">Klaus Schulze</a> - The Wisdom of the Leaves, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Contemporary_Works_II\">Contemporary Works II</a> (2002), <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/YouTube\">YouTube</a> Video</li></ul>\n<dl><dd> <div class='embedvideo ev_inline ev_top autoResize' style=' width: 646px;'><div class='embedvideowrap' style='width: 640px;'><iframe src=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/rgWN8OkdjL4?\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe></div></div></dd></dl>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Leaf_Node&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a href=\"/Category:M._C._Escher\" title=\"Category:M. C. Escher\">M. C. Escher</a>, Dewdrop, 1948, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.mcescher.com/Gallery/gallery-back.htm\">Picture gallery \"Back in Holland 1941 - 1954\"</a> from <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.mcescher.com/\">The Official M.C. Escher Website</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/Node\" title=\"Node\">Up one Level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260301140935\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.018 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.020 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 34/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 98/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 26/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key oscar70_mw1-mw_:pcache:idhash:1059-0!canonical and timestamp 20260301140935 and revision id 5713\n -->\n"
